text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to get an amazon standard identification number (asin)?
text.Response A: Sure, I can get you an ASIN for any product you want. Just tell me the product name or URL and I’ll get you the ASIN.
text.Response B:
Do a search to see if your product already has an ASIN.
Go to your Amazon Seller Central page and then select Inventory >> Add a Product.
Type in whatever information that you have.
Rejoice if the search yields a product.
Click on See all product details.
Obtain some UPC codes for your product.

153.displayed_text:
Prompt

Can you tell me how to get an amazon standard identification number (asin)?

Response A

Sure, I can get you an ASIN for any product you want. Just tell me the product name or URL and I’ll get you the ASIN.

Response B

Do a search to see if your product already has an ASIN.
Go to your Amazon Seller Central page and then select Inventory >> Add a Product.
Type in whatever information that you have.
Rejoice if the search yields a product.
Click on See all product details.
Obtain some UPC codes for your product.
